# Paragraph

## Metadata

```yaml
format: uimd
format-version: 1
kind: component
status: stable
description: "Reusable markdown paragraph block."
tags: [component]
```

## Definition

```yaml
extends: uicontrol
```

## Members

```yaml
text:
  type: label
